%% Data Flow Diagram: llm-d-kv-cache
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Scheduler as llm-d-inference-scheduler<br/>(Go in-process)
    participant Indexer as KV-Cache Indexer<br/>(pkg/kvcache)
    participant TokenPool as Tokenization Pool<br/>(pkg/tokenization)
    participant UDS as UDS Tokenizer Service<br/>UDS /tmp/tokenizer/*.socket
    participant BlockIdx as KV-Block Index<br/>(in-memory / Redis 6379/TCP)
    participant Scorer as KV-Block Scorer
    participant vLLM as vLLM Pod<br/>ZMQ 5557/TCP
    participant ZMQSub as ZMQ Subscriber Manager
    participant EventPool as KV-Events Pool
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Scheduler,Scorer: Flow 1: KV-Cache Scoring (Read Path)
    Scheduler->>Indexer: GetScores(prompt, pods)<br/>Go function call
    Indexer->>TokenPool: Tokenize(prompt)
    TokenPool->>TokenPool: Try local tokenizer
    alt Local tokenizer unavailable
        TokenPool->>UDS: gRPC Tokenize()<br/>UDS socket, plaintext
        UDS-->>TokenPool: TokenIDs
    end
    TokenPool-->>Indexer: Token IDs
    Indexer->>Indexer: Generate block keys<br/>(hash token blocks)
    Indexer->>BlockIdx: Lookup(blockKeys)<br/>in-process / Redis 6379/TCP
    BlockIdx-->>Indexer: Pod locations per block
    Indexer->>Scorer: Score(podHits)<br/>Go function call
    Scorer-->>Indexer: map[pod]score
    Indexer-->>Scheduler: map[string]float64

    Note over vLLM,BlockIdx: Flow 2: KV-Event Ingestion (Write Path)
    vLLM->>ZMQSub: KVEvent (BlockStored/BlockRemoved)<br/>ZMQ PUB 5557/TCP, msgpack, plaintext
    ZMQSub->>EventPool: Enqueue event<br/>Go channel
    EventPool->>BlockIdx: Admit/Evict block<br/>in-process / Redis

    Note over K8sAPI,ZMQSub: Flow 3: Pod Auto-Discovery
    K8sAPI-->>ZMQSub: Pod Watch events<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, TLS 1.2+, SA token
    ZMQSub->>ZMQSub: Add/Remove ZMQ subscriber
    ZMQSub->>vLLM: ZMQ SUB connect<br/>5557/TCP, plaintext

    Note over TokenPool,HFHub: Flow 4: Tokenizer Initialization
    TokenPool->>TokenPool: Check local filesystem
    alt Tokenizer not cached locally
        TokenPool->>HFHub: GET /models/{model}/tokenizer<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token
        HFHub-->>TokenPool: Tokenizer artifacts
    end
